text: Ruan Terblanche (born 14 March 2001) is a South African cricketer. He made his first-class debut for Boland in the 2018–19 CSA 3-Day Provincial Cup on 28 March 2019. He made his List A debut on 17 November 2019, for Boland in the 2019–20 CSA Provincial One-Day Challenge. ==References== ==External links== * Category:2001 births Category:Living people Category:South African cricketers Category:Boland cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
